pageTeslaCoil.description=The Tesla Coil is a monument of engineering, it will accept RF in through the bottom and convert to Tesla energy and transmit it via its head piece to nearby machines and devices.
pageTeslaCoil.moreInfo=The Tesla Coil has a side effect called death, it will hurt and ignite you if you come in contact with a bolt of energy. To prevent accidental death or personal injury wear a pair of Faraday Armor, bolts also can kill mobs and charge creepers.

pageAdvancedCrafter.description=The Advanced Crafter is the start machine you will need to begin Modern Alchemy, it will it will consume 100 RF/t and acts like a furnace and crafter of Steel Ingots, Actinium Ore to Dust and Wires.
pageAdvancedCrafter.moreInfo=The Advanced Crafter has four modes: Enriching, Extruding, Bending, and Furnace. Toggle each mode by pressing the button to the left of the input field.

pageBellows.description=The Electric Bellows is used to produce compressed air for the Arc Furnace Multiblock.

pageAmalgamator.description=The Amalgamator is used to produce the Replication Medium that is used in the Replicator Multiblock for the replication process.

pagePatternRecorder.description=The Pattern Recorder is used to produce the patterns that are used in the Replicator Multiblock to replicate items.
